  <summary date="2024-02-05T20:07:10Z" status="Introduced in House">Power of the Mint Act 

This bill prohibits the Board of Governors of the Federal Reserve from issuing a central bank digital currency. Further, the Department of the Treasury is prohibited from directing the board to issue a central bank digital currency.</summary>
